  "name": "Modify Onset",
  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/affliction_16.jpg",
  "data": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, you can increase the onset time of poisons you use by up to 1 hour per level. At 9th level, you can alter a poison so that it does not have an onset time, but you can trigger it as a&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/combat#TOC-Swift-Actions\">swift action</a>&nbsp;to take effect at any time, regardless of distance. If you do not trigger this&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions/poison\">poison</a>&nbsp;within 1 week of poisoning a target, the&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions/poison\">poison</a>&nbsp;dissipates harmlessly. The&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions/poison\">poison</a>&nbsp;can be detected and removed before it is triggered using any normal methods of detecting and removing&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.d20pfsrd.com/gamemastering/afflictions/poison\">poison</a>.</p>"
    },
